ustralia)|NBL]]\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|4th\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|30\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|17\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|13\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|0.567\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|Lost in Elimination-Finals to [[West Sydney Razorbacks]], 2\u20130 ([[playoff format|series]])\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|[[Alan Black (basketball)|Alan Black]]\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|[[Andrew Vlahov]]\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|[[Ricky Grace]]\n|-\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|[[2002\u201303 NBL season|2002\u201303]]\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|1\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|[[National Basketball League (Australia)|NBL]]\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"bgcolor=silver|2nd \n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|30\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|22\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|8\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|0.733 \n|style=\"text-align:center;\"bgcolor=silver|Runner-Up in Final against [[Sydney Kings]], 2\u20130 ([[playoff format|series]])\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|[[Alan Black (basketball)|Alan Black]]\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|[[Ricky Grace]]\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|[[Rob Feaster]]\n|-\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|[[2003\u201304 NBL season|2003\u201304]]\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|1\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|[[National Basketball League (Australia)|NBL]]\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|7th\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|33\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|15\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|18\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|0.455 \n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|Lost in Elimination-Finals to [[Cairns Taipans]], 103\u201396\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|[[Mike Ellis (basketball)|Mike Ellis]]\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|[[Ricky Grace]]\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|[[Rashad Tucker]]\n|-\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|[[2004\u201305 NBL season|2004\u201305]]\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|1\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|[[National Basketball League (Australia)|NBL]]\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|7th\n|style=