=Donaldson|first=Mark|url=http://www.communitynews.com.au/joondalup-times/sport/perth-wildcats-mike-ellis-and-greg-hire-reflect-on-influence-of-scott-fentons-death/|title=Perth Wildcats: Mike Ellis and Greg Hire reflect on influence of Scott Fenton\u2019s death|work=CommunityNews.com.au|date=29 November 2012|accessdate=8 March 2017}}</ref>\n\n===30th Anniversary All-Star Team===\nOn 4 February 2013, the Perth Wildcats announced their best team from the first three decades of the franchise at their 30th anniversary breakfast. The team was picked by 1995 championship coach [[Adrian Hurley]], ''The West Australian''{{'}}s online sports editor Ross Lewis, and long-time basketball broadcaster John Gardiner.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.wildcats.com.au/article/id/1cxbazj9qynox119hepd4i378d |title=30th Anniversary All-Star Team |work=Wildcats.com.au |date=4 February 2013 |accessdate=16 November 2014 |url-status=bot: unknown |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131211212023/http://www.wildcats.com.au/article/id/1cxbazj9qynox119hepd4i378d |archivedate=11 December 2013 }}</ref>\n\n*Coach: Adrian Hurley\n*General Manager: [[Cal Bruton]]\n{| style=\"text-align: center; background:red; color:black\"\n!width=\"40\"|Pos.\n!width=\"185\"|Starter\n!width=\"185\"|Bench\n|-style=\"height:40px; background:white; color:black\"\n! style=\"background:black\" | {{ font color | red | C | link=Center (basketball) }}\n| [[James Crawford (basketball)|James Crawford]] || [[Paul Rogers (basketball)|Paul Rogers]]\n|-style=\"height:40px; background:white; color:black\"\n! style=\"background:black\" | {{ font color | red | PF | link=Power forward (basketball) }}\n| [[Scott Fisher (basketball)|Scott Fisher]] || [[Kendal Pinder]]\n|-style=\"height:40px; background:white; color:black\"\n! style=\"background:black\" | {{ font color | red | SF | link=Small forward }}\n| [[Andrew Vlahov]] (c) || [[Shawn Redhage]]\n|-style=\"height:40px; background:white; color:black\"\n! style=\"background:black\" 